{
  "video_id": "5qzy1fHYQNg",
  "title": "Let's launch a satellite to track a threatening greenhouse gas | Fred Krupp",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13230.0,
      "end_time": 16770.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got a big problem on our hands with global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16794.0,
      "end_time": 21815.0,
      "text": "A lot of you, a lot of people have been watching the floods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21839.0,
      "end_time": 24238.0,
      "text": "the droughts, the storms, the fires."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26712.0,
      "end_time": 30434.0,
      "text": "When I leave this stage today, I don&#39;t want you to have hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 32520.000000000004,
      "end_time": 36530.0,
      "text": "I want you to have certainty, real certainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 36770.0,
      "end_time": 40529.0,
      "text": "that we can make a dent in this problem and live to see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 42460.0,
      "end_time": 45387.0,
      "text": "I want to give you a vision of what that would look like."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 46736.0,
      "end_time": 49768.0,
      "text": "This is the first time we&#39;ve shared this publicly."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 50498.0,
      "end_time": 52720.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re the first audience to hear it."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 54204.0,
      "end_time": 56585.0,
      "text": "We are going to launch a rocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 57347.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "And on that rocket will be a satellite."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 59284.0,
      "end_time": 62766.0,
      "text": "And that satellite will collect data about pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 62790.0,
      "end_time": 64590.0,
      "text": "that is warming the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 65441.0,
      "end_time": 68442.0,
      "text": "We will put that data in the hands of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 68466.0,
      "end_time": 72125.0,
      "text": "who can make simple fixes"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 72149.0,
      "end_time": 76144.0,
      "text": "that will change the course of global warming in our lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 77592.0,
      "end_time": 81219.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a lot to take in, maybe I should back up."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 81626.0,
      "end_time": 83612.0,
      "text": "First, let me introduce myself, I&#39;m Fred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 83636.0,
      "end_time": 86720.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been an environmentalist since I was a kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 86960.0,
      "end_time": 89611.0,
      "text": "when I watched the fish and the frogs in my neighborhood pond"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 89635.0,
      "end_time": 91369.0,
      "text": "die from a chemical spill."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 92673.0,
      "end_time": 93940.0,
      "text": "That bothered me."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 94728.0,
      "end_time": 100777.0,
      "text": "Later, a professor inspired me to think about environmentalism differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 101542.0,
      "end_time": 104836.0,
      "text": "How the best solutions come from"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 104860.0,
      "end_time": 107566.0,
      "text": "answering people&#39;s aspirations for prosperity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 107590.0,
      "end_time": 112874.0,
      "text": "things like being safe and healthy and thriving in this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 114140.0,
      "end_time": 118345.0,
      "text": "So I joined the Environmental Defense Fund to build those kind of solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 119296.0,
      "end_time": 123875.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve worked my whole career for a moment like this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 123899.0,
      "end_time": 127593.0,
      "text": "the moment, when we can stop fighting headwinds"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 127617.0,
      "end_time": 130283.0,
      "text": "and start to have the wind at our backs."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 130949.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133617.0,
      "text": "Because of the power of information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 133641.0,
      "end_time": 135950.0,
      "text": "information from technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 135974.0,
      "end_time": 139390.0,
      "text": "that is coming down in price and going up in precision."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 141140.0,
      "end_time": 144815.0,
      "text": "You see, there&#39;s something about climate change that we didn&#39;t grasp"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 144839.0,
      "end_time": 146188.0,
      "text": "just a decade ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 146855.0,
      "end_time": 150947.0,
      "text": "The world was so focused on carbon dioxide"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 150971.0,
      "end_time": 154288.0,
      "text": "that we overlooked another important gas."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 154312.0,
      "end_time": 156245.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t appreciate methane."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 157236.0,
      "end_time": 160283.0,
      "text": "Methane pollution causes one quarter of the global warming"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 160307.0,
      "end_time": 162573.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re experiencing right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 163641.0,
      "end_time": 168317.0,
      "text": "Pound for pound, its immediate impact is far greater than carbon dioxide."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 169173.0,
      "end_time": 173797.0,
      "text": "Eighty four times greater over a 20-year period."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 176220.0,
      "end_time": 178594.0,
      "text": "One of the largest sources of methane pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 178618.0,
      "end_time": 180484.0,
      "text": "is the oil and gas industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 181380.0,
      "end_time": 184638.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not obvious, because methane is invisible."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 185411.0,
      "end_time": 188299.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a look at this natural gas storage facility"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 188323.0,
      "end_time": 190530.0,
      "text": "outside of Los Angeles."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 190657.0,
      "end_time": 192257.0,
      "text": "Can you see the methane?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 194220.0,
      "end_time": 195172.0,
      "text": "Neither can I."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 195783.0,
      "end_time": 196933.0,
      "text": "How about now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 197530.0,
      "end_time": 201672.0,
      "text": "We shot this using an infrared camera, at the same spot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 201696.0,
      "end_time": 206256.0,
      "text": "exposing one of the worst methane leaks in the history of the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 206847.0,
      "end_time": 208823.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a very different picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 209251.0,
      "end_time": 213910.0,
      "text": "It turns out that natural gas is displacing our dependance on coal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 213934.0,
      "end_time": 216672.0,
      "text": "which emits far more carbon dioxide."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 217466.0,
      "end_time": 219847.0,
      "text": "But natural gas is mostly methane."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 220427.0,
      "end_time": 222966.0,
      "text": "So, as it&#39;s produced and processed"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 222991.0,
      "end_time": 227538.0,
      "text": "and transported to homes and businesses across America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 227562.0,
      "end_time": 233670.0,
      "text": "it escapes from wells and pipes and other equipment."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 233435.0,
      "end_time": 236213.0,
      "text": "It gets up into the sky and contributes"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 236237.0,
      "end_time": 239304.0,
      "text": "to the disasters that we&#39;re now experiencing."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 240467.0,
      "end_time": 242467.0,
      "text": "That does not have to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 243712.0,
      "end_time": 245727.0,
      "text": "But nobody had paid much attention to it"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 245752.0,
      "end_time": 249489.0,
      "text": "until we launched a nationwide study to understand the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 250610.0,
      "end_time": 256513.0,
      "text": "We used drones, planes, helicopters, even Google Street View cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 256536.0,
      "end_time": 259933.0,
      "text": "It turns out there&#39;s far more of this methane pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 259958.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261991.00000000003,
      "text": "than what the government is reporting."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 262789.0,
      "end_time": 269488.0,
      "text": "It also turns out that when we find where the gas is being vented and leaked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 269512.0,
      "end_time": 273656.0,
      "text": "most of those sources can be fixed easily and inexpensively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 273680.0,
      "end_time": 277280.0,
      "text": "saving the gas that would have otherwise been wasted."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 278116.0,
      "end_time": 283299.0,
      "text": "And finally, we learn that when you put information like that into people&#39;s hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 283323.0,
      "end_time": 284472.0,
      "text": "they act."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 285680.0,
      "end_time": 289815.0,
      "text": "Leading companies replaced valves and tightened loose-fitting pipes."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 290393.0,
      "end_time": 294649.0,
      "text": "Colorado became the first state in the nation to limit methane pollution;"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 294673.0,
      "end_time": 298730.0,
      "text": "California followed suit, and the public joined in."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 299967.0,
      "end_time": 303498.0,
      "text": "Tweets started flying -- #cutmethane."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 304825.0,
      "end_time": 307625.0,
      "text": "And everybody&#39;s paying more attention now."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 309940.0,
      "end_time": 315552.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re doing this because we can&#39;t wait for Washington, especially not now."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 316847.0,
      "end_time": 322219.0,
      "text": "In fact, we have to take what we&#39;ve done so far"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 322244.0,
      "end_time": 324283.0,
      "text": "and go higher, to the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 325371.0,
      "end_time": 329751.0,
      "text": "The United Stated represents about 10 percent of this pollution."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 330308.0,
      "end_time": 332908.0,
      "text": "To find the rest, we have to go global."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 333911.0,
      "end_time": 335616.0,
      "text": "Remember that rocket I mentioned?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 335640.0,
      "end_time": 339770.0,
      "text": "It will launch a compact satellite, called MethaneSAT,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 339101.0,
      "end_time": 343850.0,
      "text": "to do what no one has been able to do until now:"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 343109.0,
      "end_time": 348212.0,
      "text": "measure methane pollution from oil and gas facilities worldwide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 348236.0,
      "end_time": 350116.0,
      "text": "with exacting precision."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 350664.0,
      "end_time": 354156.0,
      "text": "Its data stream will allow us to map that pollution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 354180.0,
      "end_time": 356470.0,
      "text": "so that everyone can see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 356712.0,
      "end_time": 359920.0,
      "text": "Then it&#39;s all about turning data into action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 359117.0,
      "end_time": 361489.0,
      "text": "just as we did in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 361513.0,
      "end_time": 366727.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve seen that when we present companies with data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 366752.0,
      "end_time": 369152.0,
      "text": "many of them will cut the pollution."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 370379.0,
      "end_time": 373434.0,
      "text": "Citizens will be empowered to take action;"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 373458.0,
      "end_time": 376258.0,
      "text": "governments will tighten the regulations."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 377331.0,
      "end_time": 381149.0,
      "text": "And because all of our data will be free and public,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 381173.0,
      "end_time": 382554.0,
      "text": "there will be transparency --"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 382578.0,
      "end_time": 387220.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll all be to see how much progress is being made and where."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 387609.0,
      "end_time": 389450.0,
      "text": "Which brings me to our goal:"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 389474.0,
      "end_time": 394719.0,
      "text": "to cut this methane pollution by 45 percent by 2025."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 395526.0,
      "end_time": 402363.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 402387.0,
      "end_time": 405982.0,
      "text": "That will have the same near-term impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 406600.0,
      "end_time": 410426.0,
      "text": "as shutting down 1,300 coal-fired power plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 411482.0,
      "end_time": 415548.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s one third of all the coal-fired power plants in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 415997.0,
      "end_time": 420983.0,
      "text": "Nothing else can have this sort of near-term impact at such a low cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 422302.0,
      "end_time": 424945.0,
      "text": "The fact that a single satellite"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 424969.0,
      "end_time": 429655.0,
      "text": "can help us put the brakes on global warming is truly remarkable."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 430482.0,
      "end_time": 434823.0,
      "text": "This is our chance to create change in our lifetimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 434847.0,
      "end_time": 436743.0,
      "text": "and we can do it now."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 437648.0,
      "end_time": 440482.0,
      "text": "Thanks to the generous giving of the Audacious Project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 440506.0,
      "end_time": 442705.0,
      "text": "we are on a path toward liftoff."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 443665.0,
      "end_time": 447641.0,
      "text": "But my time is running short, and I promised you a vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 447665.0,
      "end_time": 450738.0,
      "text": "of what a critical piece of the solution would look like."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 452744.0,
      "end_time": 453894.0,
      "text": "Can you see it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 455378.0,
      "end_time": 457426.0,
      "text": "Can you see how this satellite leverages"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 457450.0,
      "end_time": 461200.0,
      "text": "the best of science and data and technology?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 462252.0,
      "end_time": 465482.0,
      "text": "Can you see we&#39;re entering a whole new era of innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 465506.0,
      "end_time": 467571.0,
      "text": "that is supercharging progress?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 467998.0,
      "end_time": 470331.0,
      "text": "Can you see that it&#39;s in our hands?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 471752.0,
      "end_time": 475291.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve set an aggressive goal of three years till liftoff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 475315.0,
      "end_time": 479198.0,
      "text": "and when that satellite is ready, we&#39;ll have a launch party."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 480284.0,
      "end_time": 481817.0,
      "text": "A literal launch party."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 483300.0,
      "end_time": 488375.0,
      "text": "So imagine a blue-sky day, crowds of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 488399.0,
      "end_time": 490299.0,
      "text": "television cameras,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 490323.0,
      "end_time": 492856.0,
      "text": "kids staring up toward the sky"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 492880.0,
      "end_time": 495303.0,
      "text": "at a thing that will change their future."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 496117.0,
      "end_time": 498317.0,
      "text": "What an amazing day that will be."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 498752.0,
      "end_time": 500819.0,
      "text": "What a big opportunity we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 501514.0,
      "end_time": 502664.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t wait."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 503370.0,
      "end_time": 504188.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 504212.0,
      "end_time": 509619.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}